Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.51,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(306,198)}{\i1}Kaga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.51,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(299,232)}{\i1}Kouko{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:14.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But since coming here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:21.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I've become invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:27.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:32.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where is everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:35.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's nearly time, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, did you tell Mitsuo about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:41.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I texted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He just sent me this reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.00,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(325,142)}Yanagisawa Mitsuo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.00,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(254,184)}No subject
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.00,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(233,244)}An overnight trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.00,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(237,274)}With which club?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's thinking about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:51.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:55.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,2D-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you here for the trip, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"2D-kun"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is "2" his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I met him the other day at the tea club's welcoming party...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you okay, 2D-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-you're Kaga Kouko-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've seen you in our civil law class!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:20.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:25.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My real name is Sato Takaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:29.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was named 2D-kun at the tea club's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Gather 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Our three-day, two-night trip begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:38.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank y-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:39.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you start...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,by writing your name, address, and phone number on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:46.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, you can fill them out in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:47.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're a little behind schedule, so we'll have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:53.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, you're in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:54.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:02.75,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(284,314)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Night Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:09.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stop my heart from dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:15.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Crying and laughing, we never forget our memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:26.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Finding your true self
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:29.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And becoming an adult is difficult work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:32.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I can forget for now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The night is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:40.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As our hearts beat excitedly in rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And we frolic about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:46.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I nearly realize
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:50.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The feelings I want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:53.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if we are afraid of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You cannot move if you remain empty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:03.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all right if we have fun, so let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:07.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I forget all my troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:10.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and dance the night away with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:17.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll become someone more wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This endless Golden Time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The distance between us as you approach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:27.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Neither closes nor widens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:31.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll treasure this even it it's the long way around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.81,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(157,81)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}PERSONAL INFORMATION FORM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.81,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(344,128)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}University/Department:{\i1}FUKURAI UNIVERSITY LAW{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.81,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(183,170)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}School Name:{\i1}TADA BANRI{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.81,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(207,213)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Residence:{\i1}TOKYO SUGINAMI{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so glad the weather's nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, let me know if you want a drink or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We won't be making any stops, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so maybe you shouldn't drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh... Your name's Kaga Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What a beautiful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you looking around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hurry up and fill in your form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.74,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(179,303)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Fukurai University
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.74,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(169,340)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Fuji Seminar House
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but didn't we just pass the seminar house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Didn't we just pass our university's seminar house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Didn't we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Get ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Carsick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to collect your forms now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Give me your completed forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.90,Dialogue10,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(222,174)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}PERSONAL INFORMATION FORM{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.90,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(166,207)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}University/Department: FUKURAI UNIVERSITY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.90,Dialogue11,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(354,236)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}LITERATURE DEPT{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.90,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(285,303)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Name: TAKAHASHI SHU{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, good. I can finally talk to someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is this really the university's seminar house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My phone has no service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:22.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:37.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The place was the training facility for a religious organization I had never heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll keep all your luggage in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Bring your bags on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:06:00.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,For the next five hours, maybe longer, we were shown films...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:05.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and indoctrinated with lectures on the universe and souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't handle being trapped here another two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Lift your glasses, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:32.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,To the awakening of our new children,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,to the excellent full moon tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and to our reunion ten thousand years into a future century!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello, Neo-Children!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They made us write down our addresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're throwing a party for the day of your awakening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Try to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:59.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You must begin by loving the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Have you ever loved the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:02.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:05.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm responsible for bringing Kaga-san here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:09.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need to at least get her home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What should I do? How can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:20.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ten thousand years into a future century?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You tricked us by calling yourselves a club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, aren't you detaining us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:25.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take us home immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We don't want to be here any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll sue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's what everyone says at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll understand soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:45.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After spending all day tomorrow speaking with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll awaken, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you people serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you want to leave, then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't want to go, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you talking about, Tada Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your whining is bringing everyone down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you not like about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Having difficult people like you around just makes trouble for the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to have fun here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:11.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Quit complaining over little things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Senpai, they're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If they want to leave, you should let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:22.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I saw that film earlier, I was really moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:29.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd like to listen to what you have to say in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:36.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In high school, I suffered a serious injury in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and lost all my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's what you'd call amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:46.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I awoke, I was in a world full of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I had no parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No friends, no acquaintances... no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:57.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...and so insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was in such pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But you don't need to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The moment of your salvation has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:13.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I believe we should allow the kids who are not interested to depart,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and instead spend time getting to know this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go back with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've already decided to become a believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Kaga-san,\NI met some good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:31.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you're leaving, get in the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I decided to stay after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was impressed by the lecture earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even though I'm beautiful, I'm not very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have abandoned this century.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I long for the new century!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We somehow managed to meet our quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now we can save face with the district leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're ruining the whole reason I stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I knew that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:25.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You wasted your chance to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I couldn't leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:33.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's my fault you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's escape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The stars shouldn't be waiting in the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come here so we can tell you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:48.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, but first...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'd like to put her luggage away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Could we borrow the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The key?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:55.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:07.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Somebody! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:18.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They locked the door from the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:21.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think we can get out through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hey, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:24.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're trying to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, someone bring the spare key!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can we leave everything except your valuables?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:35.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They should be heading towards the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Split up and search!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We passed our university's seminar house on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:59.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If we can make it there,\NI'm sure the rest will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We seem to have lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.53,Dialogue14,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(393,112)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}OUT OF{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.53,Dialogue12,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(393,142)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}SERVICE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I still can't get any service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What about yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mine's not working either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's my fault this happened, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm the one who had the flyer, and I'm the one they approached.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You just came along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:57.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought it would be nice if you could make friends in this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:58.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It really isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It really isn't your fault, Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:20.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought you would tell me about Mitsuo if I became friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've never cared about clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's true no one tried to recruit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:31.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's true everyone at college ignores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But it didn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:40.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was only trying to win your sympathy by appearing depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted information about Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you really were after Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, Yanao...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I mixed them up. Mitsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was for Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:55.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,90%, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:57.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What about the other 10%?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:08.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All I know for sure is that you're the only one who talks to me at college, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was happy you talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:19.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I bet Yana-san's worried about you right now, Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't tell him any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:22.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:28.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,His uncertain feelings will change to a passionate possessiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and you'll be sitting firmly in Yana-san's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No way! That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Will that really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:40.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san will realize just how important his childhood friend is to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:44.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I thought she was annoying."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I even suspected her of being a stalker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:51.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"However, this girl truly is the one I'm destined to marry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Kouko!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Mitsuo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:11.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does Yana-san know that side of you, Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:13.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:18.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You seem a little different when Yana-san isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:24.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san hasn't seen you laugh that much, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you think I seem different...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:31.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm complete when I'm with Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Think of that as the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you mean, complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:40.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm nothing without Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:49.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wake up, go to sleep, go to school, dress up, cry, and laugh because of Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Without Mitsuo, I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:57.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's no reason for me to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:02.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, you really are all about Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's how I've always lived my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:09.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have nothing better to do than chase a man who ignores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You must think I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:15.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fine, though. I really am stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do things that upset him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like hitting him with roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:23.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo's fault! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was clearly your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There was a reason for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:34.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Four months of rage exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:39.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The truth is, I meant to congratulate him and hand over the roses with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was my perfect plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What did you think would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought for sure I'd knock Mitsuo out this time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,with my bravery in following him to the same university!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:59.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo always told me he would apply to our affiliated university.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I knew it was a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:05.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I pretended to be deceived, and secretly applied to the same school as Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:10.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I hoped he would eventually tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:15.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But even after we graduated, he didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:19.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I still meant to forgive him with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:25.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But on the day of the entrance ceremony, when I saw him happily walking up with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:29.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just couldn't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why you whacked him with the roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's right, wham!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I regret it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right. I keep giving him reasons to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:49.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When it comes to Mitsuo,\NI can't keep a cool head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I lose sight of everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's not talk about me.\NTell me about yourself, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, are you going out with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I really did lose my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:18.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The day after I graduated from high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I apparently fell off a bridge in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:24.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I lost my memories after that, and here I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:29.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I forgot everything I knew about myself before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:37.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My relationships with parents, friends, classmates, and teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What I liked and didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In other words, I lost what you'd call my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:46.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even a year in the hospital and rehabilitation didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was afraid to meet my old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought the one they wanted to see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,was the former Tada Banri they knew before I lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:02.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I felt like they didn't need who I was now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I refused to meet anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:11.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But if I had a girlfriend, I'm sure she'd have come to see me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:21.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't remember anything, but sometimes these emotions come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sort of like nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like I can almost remember something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But when I try to pursue those feelings, they disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's like there's something written on a piece of paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and when I try to read it, the sentence disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:46.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Those vague hints of memories\NI can almost recall are just eaten away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:50.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's actually quite terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry! That must have been weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly healthy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you have any questions, ask away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In that case, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:20.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you want to return to your past self?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The only self I know is the person I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:34.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I understand why my parents and other people want me to return to my old self, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:38.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sometimes I want to try returning to my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:43.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That is, I wouldn't mind adding my past memories to my present self,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:46.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but to lose my current identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:50.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If my present self had to disappear and be replaced by my old self, I wouldn't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The old Tada Banri disappeared from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:21:00.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The person here now is a new and different Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:13.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wonder if the old Tada-kun is watching over you from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like a guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That might be a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:25.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:30.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, this is just like that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:32.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait, Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe it's those believers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:43.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If it is, we've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:46.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:47.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can't you tell? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:52.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:53.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Barbara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:55.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:19.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In one hand in the sweetened cafe latte I love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:23.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The moment I smiled I could smell love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:27.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to wear my cherry-colored dress perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:32.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My heart beats quietly as I rush to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:35.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:37.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watch out for that sweet trap
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:39.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll whisper to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}(Hey, I'm a little anxious)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:46.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, I long for this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:50.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How should I smile when I see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:53.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pretty love, pretty love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:57.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Under the sky, under sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:00.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's hold hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:05.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't be honest about my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:10.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But pull me along by my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:40.75,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(55,410)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Blackout
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:28.17,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(260,376)}Oh! Tada Banri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:31.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(147,343)}What are you doing wearing slippers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:31.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(175,378)}way out here in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(225,379)}Oh, are you on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:35.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(301,378)}Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.61,0:23:36.78,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(333,376)}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:38.41,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(253,379)}What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:40.75,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(217,379)}Anyway, who's Barbara?
